  <title> How to Contact Me</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>
        When you need to get in touch with me, the best way to do so will be through email. 
        Please include the class &amp; section number in the subject line of your email. 
        Please note that I check and respond to emails between the hours of 8am and 5pm, 
        Mondays through Thursdays. 

